How to Use: Squalane + Copper Peptide Rapid Plumping Serum | Layering Hyaluronic Acid | Biossance
•
•
16,913 views 3 years ago
Got questions about how to use serums? Why do I need to use Hyaluronic Acid? How do I know which serum to choose? What ingredient actives should I avoid using with this serum? How do I layer skincare products? Learn all about how to choose and use the right Biossance treatment serum for you with our Director of Global Education, McKenzie and our Global Education Manager, Alexis. They'll walk you through the different Biossance serums, how to use the new Copper Peptide Rapid Plumping Serum, and how to use different treatments in your skincare routine. If you are looking for a serum that plumps and hydrates the skin reach for the Squalane + Copper Peptide Rapid Plumping Serum. If you are looking for a serum to reduce fine lines and wrinkles reach for the Squalane + Phyto-Retinol Serum. Perhaps you have dark spots or hyperpigmentation, you'll want to reach for the Squalane + Vitamin C Dark Spot Serum. Lastly, if you are looking to reduce texture and acne, reach for the Squalane + Lactic Acid Resurfacing Night Serum. Who is Biossance? We are the leaders in the science ofbeauty. We were inspired to use innovative biotechnology to make a positive impact on the world. From our original breakthrough—creating sugarcane squalane—to the ingredient innovation in each and every skincare product, Biossance's mission is to use the power of biotechnology to create effective skincare that is also gentle on the planet we share. Join our community of changemakers and let’s make tomorrow better.
